<br>
The event would be the RP, questing and fighting.<br>
<br>
The event's story line would be the plot to take down a god. (no, this is NOT set in stone)<br>
<br>
<b><i>If good guys do not show up to save the day</b></i>, then Evil wins and it should go down in the history of the EMarr server as such... until there is a day that good regroups and can take back what we have stolen, and return to the EMarr server it's Valor, Honor, Courage, Love and whatever else.  The same applies if Evil does not show up to do their thing, though from the looks of things, Evil is more than ready to act on this. =)<br>
